185
00:13:49,686 --> 00:13:52,689
I despise you.

186
00:13:52,689 --> 00:13:54,691
チャーリー

187
00:13:54,691 --> 00:13:58,695
I despise you.

188
00:13:58,695 --> 00:14:03,695
I despise you... despise you.

189
